(25, 'Device', 24, 'How can i connect my device to web?', 'You can do this manually by consulting the specific configuration guides for your device, available in the &quot;Set up online&quot;, selecting from the menu on the make and model.\r\nIf you do not remember the specific model of your Smartphone or Tablet, you can check it entering MyCIM Mobile. Your device will be automatically detected and you can display make and model.', -1),
(26, 'Device', -1, 'How can i activate a house line?', 'Request activation of a home phone line is very simple, you can:\r\napply online\r\ncall customer service fixed line 187\r\nbring to you at a CIM Shop.\r\nCheck the activation mode by consulting the various deals available on line.', -1),
